The dictionary form is the same structure `to_json()` serializes, so `gw.Surv.from_dict()`
rebuilds an equivalent response from it.

::: {#01332ef7 .cell execution_count=15}
``` {.python .cell-code}
# Serialize to a dict, then immediately reconstruct from it
gw.Surv.from_dict(gw.Surv.right([5, 6, 4], event=[1, 0, 1]).to_dict())
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=14}
```
Surv(type=right, n=3, events=2)
```
:::
